<task id="how-to-use-zero-size-indent">
    <title>How to use zero size indent</title>
    <shortdesc/>
    <taskbody>
        <context>
            <p>When you use pretty print, or when you save a document from the
          <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol>, <ph><ph keyref="product"/></ph> allows you to use zero size
        indent. To stop indenting text depending on the depth of the nodes in an XML document:</p>
        </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Go to <menucascade>
                        <uicontrol>Option</uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol> Preferences</uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol> Editor</uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol> Format</uicontrol>
                    </menucascade>;</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Disable <uicontrol>Detect indent on option</uicontrol>;</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Set <uicontrol>Indent size</uicontrol> to zero. </cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
